Auklet for Python
=================
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/auklet.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/auklet
    :alt: PyPi page link -- version

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/auklet.svg
